Subject: [PATCH 12/14] arm64: mm: Set PSTATE.PAN from the cpu_enable_pan()
 call

commit 7209c868600bd8926e37c10b9aae83124ccc1dd8 upstream.

Commit 338d4f49d6f7 ("arm64: kernel: Add support for Privileged Access
